# Simple Library Management System

Platform: C

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Features:

- Library Books/Student records Management
- Console UI
- Multiple small files are connected to each other by specifying path(make the working/ programming easier).
- File Handling (to store records of books and student)
- Save Books Record in .DAT file.
